#- Author's Note:
-------------------

I have spent the better part of my CivCraft life in Haven. It should go without saying that its my favourite city. The community we have here is great and ever growing. I hope to stay part of  it for as long as I can.
#- Author's Note:
-------------------

You all make the terrible things that happen on this server a whole lot more bearable.

Haven will never die.
(Hobo's words)

